snippet.title: Stan Winston School
snippet.description:
IMAGINE. LEARN. CREATE. Online Courses by Hollywood's Masters Artists

Stan Winston School inspires and fosters creativity through online training with Hollywood's leading artists and technical wizards. Featuring hundreds of hours of On-Demand video instruction, the SWSCA Course Library offers students around the world the professional knowledge and tools they need to bring their imagination to life.

Welcome to our Official YouTube Channel! SUBSCRIBE & Explore.

WHAT YOU'LL FIND HERE:

• "Movie Magic" Behind-the-Scenes Videos
• On-Demand & Live Course Previews
• Free Character Creation Course Chapters
• Monster Maker Interviews with Hollywood Legends
• Fan Features & Artist Spotlights

BE SURE TO VISIT OUR WEBSITE FOR IN-DEPTH ONLINE INSTRUCTION IN THE ART & TECHNOLOGY OF CHARACTER CREATION!
